      "output": "\r\n    Computer: AndieKobbie-OMEN\r\n    Description: \r\n  Service stopped.\r\n  \r\n  Event[24]:\r\n    Log Name: Application\r\n    Source: Windows Error Reporting\r\n    Date: 2026-07-04T07:13:57.8730000Z\r\n>   Event ID: 1001\r\n    Task: N/A\r\n    Level: Informazioni\r\n    Opcode: Informazioni\r\n  Stato rapporto: 268435456\r\n  Bucket con hash: f1079f02389183773e1ddf14174c7166\r\n  GUID CAB: 0\r\n  \r\n  Event[25]:\r\n    Log Name: Application\r\n    Source: Windows Error Reporting\r\n    Date: 2026-07-04T07:13:32.3030000Z\r\n>   Event ID: 1001\r\n    Task: N/A\r\n    Level: Informazioni\r\n    Opcode: Informazioni\r\n    Computer: AndieKobbie-OMEN\r\n    Description: \r\n  [21436:19588:0704/052938.976:INFO:chrome\\browser\\extensions\\extension_garbage_collector.cc:188] Garbage collection \r\nfor extensions on file thread is complete.\r\n  \r\n  Event[36]:\r\n    Log Name: Application\r\n    Source: Windows Error Reporting\r\n    Date: 2026-07-04T05:28:08.1910000Z\r\n>   Event ID: 1001\r\n    Task: N/A\r\n    Level: Informazioni\r\n    Opcode: Informazioni\r\n    Computer: AndieKobbie-OMEN\r\n    Description: \r\n  Migrazione offline di livello inferiore completata.\r\n  \r\n  Event[65]:\r\n    Log Name: Application\r\n    Source: Windows Error Reporting\r\n    Date: 2026-07-04T02:38:55.9660000Z\r\n>   Event ID: 1001\r\n    Task: N/A\r\n    Level: Informazioni\r\n    Opcode: Informazioni\r\n    Computer: AndieKobbie-OMEN\r\n    Description: \r\n  Il processo di Gestione finestre desktop � stato chiuso. (Codice di uscita processo: 0xc00001ad, conteggio riavvii: \r\n1, ID dispositivo di visualizzazione primario: Intel(R) HD Graphics 630)\r\n  \r\n  Event[72]:\r\n    Log Name: Application\r\n    Source: Windows Error Reporting\r\n    Date: 2026-07-04T01:58:17.9330000Z\r\n>   Event ID: 1001\r\n    Task: N/A\r\n    Level: Informazioni\r\n    Opcode: Informazioni\r\n    Computer: AndieKobbie-OMEN\r\n    Description: \r\n  Migrazione offline di livello inferiore completata.\r\n  \r\n  Event[76]:\r\n    Log Name: Application\r\n    Source: Windows Error Reporting\r\n    Date: 2026-07-04T01:56:54.4330000Z\r\n>   Event ID: 1001\r\n    Task: N/A\r\n    Level: Informazioni\r\n    Opcode: Informazioni\r\n    Computer: AndieKobbie-OMEN\r\n    Description: \r\n  [23456:14208:0704/014705.840:INFO:chrome\\browser\\extensions\\extension_garbage_collector.cc:188] Garbage collection \r\nfor extensions on file thread is complete.\r\n  \r\n  Event[78]:\r\n    Log Name: Application\r\n    Source: Windows Error Reporting\r\n    Date: 2026-07-04T00:54:15.9380000Z\r\n>   Event ID: 1001\r\n    Task: N/A\r\n    Level: Informazioni\r\n    Opcode: Informazioni\r\n\r\n\r\n",
      "status": "success",
